    glamor: Force GPU rendering to/from pixmaps created via DRI3
    
    Fixes crash when running DRI3 clients with ShadowPrimary enabled.
    
    Bugzilla: https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=94799
    
